These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: german, russian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:russian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:turkish is between Nationality:german and Nationality:russian##2
3. Nationality:turkish is to the east of Nationality:german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | german | turkish | russian | thai |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, banana, lemon, potato
1. Food:avocado is to the west of Food:potato##1
2. Food:banana is in an odd position##4
3. Food:banana is to the west or east of Food:avocado##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | banana | avocado | potato | lemon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: drama, martial-arts, mystery, zombie
1. Movie-Genre:zombie is to the west or east of Movie-Genre:drama##3
2. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:mystery is between Movie-Genre:zombie and Movie-Genre:martial-arts##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | mystery | martial-arts |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
