.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: avocado, peach, pineapple, strawberry
1. Food:peach == Food:peach##1
2. Food:strawberry is to the west or east of Food:pineapple##3
3. Food:pineapple is at the western end or far east##3
4. Food:avocado is in an even position##4
5. Food:strawberry is to the west of Food:peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | pineapple | strawberry | peach | avocado |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
Job: analyst, designer, manager, software-developer
1. Job:manager is in an odd position##4
2. Job:software-developer is to the west of Job:manager##1
3. Job:manager is to the west or east of Job:designer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | analyst | software-developer | manager | designer |

 